{
  "texts": [
    "The choice of the three training scenarios above is motivated by the fact that we want to evaluate the effect of two different factors on each of the training techniques:",
    "The 'English + Translations' training scenario enables the evaluation of the effect of multilinguality.",
    "In particular, we want to compare the effect of having multilingual training data against the scenario where training data is available in only one language.",
    "By translating other languages into English, we compose a dataset consisting of the same number of training examples but without having the language diversity.",
    "This eliminates the possibility that differences in performance across the three methods could be due to the size of the training data for each language."
  ]
}